messages.content: The PDF titled "Playground equipment components_REJ.pdf" pertains to a submittal document submitted by AMB Contractors, Inc. for the project PS 54X - Plaza Roofing and Play Equipment. The document includes a transmittal letter dated August 18, 2022, addressed to Abel Bainnson Butz, LLP in New York, NY, with attention to Elena Pauling, who is the A/E reviewer. The main content of the document lists playground equipment components under spec section PDS 02860.010.001, which were submitted for review but were subsequently rejected with instructions to revise and resubmit. The document outlines the responsibilities of the contractor regarding compliance with the project's specifications and drawings, and it highlights that the approval of shop drawings is only for general compliance. The document was submitted by Aslam Baig and includes specific notes on the status of the items, such as whether they are resubmittals, equal products, or alternate substitutions to the specified materials.
